      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Test sample variability (pump-to-pump geometric variation in validation hardware) is scoped out at MRL 2. The FDA GCBP validation dataset uses a single reference pump manufactured to tight tolerances; sample-to-sample variability is not a significant contributor to validation uncertainty at this risk level."
